### How to Run
1. Ensure `index.html`, `sketch.js`, `scrape.js`, and `data.json` are in the same folder.
2. Open `index.html` in a modern web browser (Safari/Chrome/Firefox).
3. Click the button in the top-left corner to begin the experience.